@startuml C1 - Process View (US Manage Representatives)
!include <C4/C4_Container>

Person(portOfficer, "Port Authority Officer")
System(api, "Port API")

' === Create Representative ===
portOfficer -> api : 1. POST /api/ShippingAgents/{taxNumber}/Representatives\n(CreateRepresentativeDTO)
api --> portOfficer : 2. 201 Created (RepresentativeDTO)

' === Update Representative ===
portOfficer -> api : 3. PUT /api/ShippingAgents/{taxNumber}/Representatives/{id}\n(UpdateRepresentativeDTO)
api --> portOfficer : 4. 200 OK (Updated RepresentativeDTO)

' === Deactivate Representative ===
portOfficer -> api : 5. POST /api/ShippingAgents/{taxNumber}/Representatives/{id}/deactivate
api --> portOfficer : 6. 204 No Content (Representative Deactivated)

@enduml
